query:
SELECT 
  id, employeeCode, name, email, corporateEmail, funcao, hierarchyLevel, managerId, userId
FROM employees 
WHERE active = 1 
AND hierarchyLevel IN ('diretoria', 'gerencia', 'coordenacao', 'supervisao')
ORDER BY 
  CASE hierarchyLevel 
    WHEN 'diretoria' THEN 1 
    WHEN 'gerencia' THEN 2 
    WHEN 'coordenacao' THEN 3 
    WHEN 'supervisao' THEN 4 
  END,
  name
LIMIT 400;
